  Some future example sets may be included from modular example files; the
  current draft still authors many examples inline in chapter source.

  The structure mirrors the four-part outline in PROJECT_PLAN.md §3.
  Part V (Predicate Logic) is planned as optional adopter content. It is
  currently commented out until those chapters are drafted.
-->
